<emphasis id="519CC5531F61FF9AFCA1F998FCE3358D" bold="true" box="[827,841,1657,1674]" pageId="42" pageNumber="321">G</emphasis>
, fruit vu de profil; 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F61FF9AFC70F998FBA0358D" bold="true" box="[1002,1034,1657,1674]" pageId="42" pageNumber="321">A -E</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F61FF9AFB8CF998FB3F358D" box="[1046,1173,1657,1674]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="321">MacKee 36587</emphasis>
(P); 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F61FF9AFFEBF971FFD635A6" bold="true" box="[113,124,1680,1697]" pageId="42" pageNumber="321">F</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F61FF9AFF1DF971FF3F35A6" bold="true" box="[135,149,1680,1697]" pageId="42" pageNumber="321">G</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F61FF9AFF05F971FEB735A6" box="[159,285,1680,1697]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="321">MacKee 30943</emphasis>
(P). Échelles: A, G, 1 cm; B-E, 3 mm; F, 1,5 cm.
